title: Walgreens Boots beats profit forecasts for third quarter
text:
09 Jul 2015 | By Edward Devlin 
Global pharmacy and health giant Walgreens Boots Alliance has beaten profit expectations in the third quarter as sales across its divisions grew following the official formation of the larger group. Available to members only
